        <section>
            <div class="container com-sp pad-bot-80 pg-inn">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="cor">
                        <div class="col-md-8">
                            <div class="cor-mid-img">
                                <img src="/client/Tuma/photos/p13.jpg" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="cor-con-mid">
                                <div class="cor-p1">
                                    <h2>Ongoing Projects</h2>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cor-p4">
                                    <p>Tumaini Senior Secondary School runs different project, which includes a piece of
                                        planned work or an activity which is finished over a period of time and intended
                                        to achieve a particular aim which help the students in one way or the other.</p>
                                    <blockquote>The projects conducted in Tumaini Senior Secondary School includes the
                                        livestock keeping, garden activity, planting trees and few month to come we
                                        expect poultry keeping. </blockquote>
                                    <p>These projects are mainly intended for the school to serve the main thing which
                                        may be required by the students during their operation in school. The projects
                                        are under control or supervision of the specific people which are mainly
                                        intended to prevent students from being involved in domesticating and other
                                        garden activities. These are only important projects which are mostly intended
                                        services to the students.</p>
                                    <h4>Livestock Keeping</h4>
                                    <p>Tumaini Senior Secondary School has introduced the new project for dairy
                                        livestock keeping. The aim of the project is supply milk to students with its
                                        staff. But also in future is to expand to other Tumaini Schools.To date, four
                                        cows, which will be expected by few months to come to give out milk. Also, all
                                        cows are freshian breed and one bull Ayrshire bull. All cattle are owned by
                                        TSSS, they feed in and out door. Under supervision of a person in charge.</p>
                                    <h4>Garden Cultivation</h4>
                                    <p>Tumaini Senior Secondary School own a garden which act as a provider of
                                        vegetables and other spices which may be required for the food. The school
                                        garden is about 1.5 acers which serves the whole school. In School, we do eat
                                        vegetable which we grow on the school garden instead of buying from the market.
                                        The school has employed the people to work on the garden instead of students
                                        working in the garden.</p>
                                    <h4>Plantation of Tree</h4>
                                    <p>Before the school closure, there is program of planting trees around the school.
                                        These involves all school staff members and students. When you move around
                                        Tumaini Senior Secondary School you find out that there many green trees around
                                        this is because the students help to irrigate the trees during summer season. In
                                        Tumaini Senior Secondary School we do encourage planting trees in order to
                                        conserve the environment.</p>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
